Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask PJMBUD1TOT [PJBUTT]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "PJMBUD1TOT" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [PJBUTT] As [SIM_]
Grizo [PJBUTT]20
Grizo [PJBUTT]40
Grizo [PJBUTT]43
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [PJBUTT]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=78 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=9
X1(1)=1 : X2(1)=78 : Y1(1)=10 : Y2(1)=12
X1(2)=1 : X2(2)=62 : Y1(2)=13 : Y2(2)=25
Return

$ON_PSCBUDQTY
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_PSCBUDQTY From W1PJMBUD1TOT
Return

$AV_PSCBUDQTY
If func SUBPJBU1T.TOTGETFMT(3)<>""
 Chgfmt [M]PSCBUDQTY(indice) With func SUBPJBU1T.TOTGETFMT(3)
Else
 Chgfmt [M]PSCBUDQTY(indice) With "-K:1X"
Endif
Gosub _AFF
Return

